          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-1" n="1">Poor Ladies! tho' their business be to Play,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-2" n="2">'Tis hard, they must be Busy Night and Day,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-3" n="3">Why shou'd they want y<hi rend="superscript">eÌ£</hi> Priviledge of Men</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-4" n="4">Nor take some small Diversions now &amp; then?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-5" n="5">Had Women, been the Makers of Our Laws,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-6" n="6">And why they were not, I can see no Cause?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-7" n="7">The Men should slave at Cards from Morn to Night.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-100M-line-8" n="8">And Female Pleasures be to Read and Write.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
